<db:section xml:id="strength-prop">
<db:title>strength : qreal</db:title>
<db:para>This property holds the strength of the effect.</db:para>
<db:para>By default, the strength is 1.0. A strength 0.0 equals to no effect, while 1.0 means full colorization.</db:para>
