<db:section xml:id="strengthChanged">
<db:title>void QGraphicsColorizeEffect::strengthChanged(qreal <db:emphasis>strength</db:emphasis>)</db:title>
<db:para>This signal is emitted whenever <db:link xlink:href="qgraphicscolorizeeffect.xml#strength-prop">setStrength</db:link>() changes the colorize strength property. <db:code role="parameter">strength</db:code> contains the new strength value of the colorize effect.</db:para>
<db:note>
<db:para>Notifier signal for property <db:link xlink:href="qgraphicscolorizeeffect.xml#strength-prop">strength</db:link>. </db:para>
